IMPLEMENTING A MICROGRAPHICS RECORDS MANAGEMENT SYSTEM.
     
DESCRIBES THE PAPERWORK STORAGE AND RETRIEVAL PROBLEMS FACED BY CMS COMPANIES
IN THE PAST; RESEARCH UNDERTAKEN TO SOLVE THE PROBLEMS AND DECISION TAKEN TO
IMPLEMENT A MICROFICHE JACKET SYSTEM. THE RESULT HAS BEEN A MASSIVE PAPERWORK
REDUCTION AND IMPROVED RECORDS MANAGEMENT SYSTEM.
